# Goal

Create a modern, lightweight, and responsive dashboard interface for "BIMBEL AGYM YUHUU". The dashboard will have a sleek, modern UI/UX (featuring a premium dark or light theme with vibrant accents and micro-animations) built with pure HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript to keep it extremely fast and lightweight without the need for heavy frameworks.

## User Review Required

Please review the proposed design aesthetic and features below. Since the requirement emphasizes "modern and lightweight", the application will be built using standard HTML/CSS/JS.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Do you prefer a **Dark Mode** aesthetic (sleek, high contrast, modern) or a **Light Mode** aesthetic (clean, bright, professional) for the dashboard? I will implement a premium look based on your preference. I will use a modern Dark Mode by default if you don't have a preference.

## Proposed Changes

We will create a Single-Page Application (SPA) feel using vanilla JS to switch views smoothly without reloading the page. All files will be placed in `c:\Users\Lenovo\Documents\BIMBEL Agym`.

### 1. Structure (`index.html`)
- **Sidebar Navigation**: Includes "BIMBEL AGYM YUHUU" branding.
  - Management User
    - Management Siswa
    - Management Guru
  - Management Bimbel
    - Tambah Kelas
    - Tambah Jadwal
- **Main Content Area**: Dynamic area that updates based on the selected sidebar menu.

### 2. Styling (`index.css`)
- **Theme**: Premium design with soft shadows, glassmorphism elements, rounded corners, and modern typography (e.g., *Inter* or *Poppins* via Google Fonts).
- **Responsiveness**: The dashboard will adapt to different screen sizes.
- **Animations**: Subtle micro-animations on hover states, button clicks, and page transitions to make the interface feel alive.

### 3. Logic & Data (`app.js`)
- **Navigation Logic**: JavaScript to handle switching between different views.
- **Data Tables**:
  - **Management Siswa**: Table with columns `[NIS, Nama Lengkap, Tgl Lahir, Jenjang, Aksi (Lihat Profil, Edit, Delete)]`.
  - **Management Guru**: Table with columns `[NIP, Nama Guru Bimbel, Mata Pelajaran, Aksi (Lihat Profil, Edit, Delete)]`.
  - *Sample data will be provided to demonstrate the UI.*
- **Forms**: Beautiful, interactive forms for "Tambah Kelas" and "Tambah Jadwal".

## Verification Plan

1. Create all files and implement the designs.
2. Use an automated browser agent to verify that the layout renders correctly.
3. Test navigation between all sections (Siswa, Guru, Tambah Kelas, Tambah Jadwal).
4. Verify that tables match the required format exactly.
5. Take a screenshot/recording of the working dashboard to show you the final result.
